{"type": "article", "id": 25440, "title": "没有时针的手表", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-14T06:59:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172403DViP12d8fF5JL3lc.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">常常能看到极简的钟表设计，这款腕表甚至取消了时针。首尔设计师 Jiwoong Jung 将腕表的背景设计成从白到黑的渐变色，黑与白的分界处则表示了小时的刻度，有渐变的光泽，就像是整个表盘在随着在选旋转。手表的整体设计简洁优雅，黄铜表环搭配皮革表带，很复古。<a href=\"http://jungjiwoong.com/?portfolio=watch\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172402vU1hTsukPI4QN6RJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172402HdD9TEvBki3NoIGf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172402ghfZSO26j4mU0VlB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172403Huj1dx9Qz7eYlFLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56479218\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}